sentences: Aneela Mirza (born 8 October 1974) is a Danish singer who has found success as a member of the pop group Toy-Box and as a solo artist under the name of "Aneela".
After the group's break-up, Aneela embarked on a solo career and released her first solo single, "Bombay Dreams", in 2005.
Aneela is married and lives in the United Kingdom.
